CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 16, 1958, pg. B2, reads: "Trio of Hikers - Golden-age picnickers enjoying recreational variety include this trio of hikers Miss Caroline Scroggs, Mrs. Annie Cook and Mrs. Rosie Wilson, striking the trail for exercise and adventure."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Caroline Scroggs, Annie Cook, and Rosie Wilson, posed near swing set in Highland Park for 30th annual outing of James East Liberty Missionary Society of Ebenezer Baptist Church
